room_title: Escape room "The Inventor's Garage" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_description: You’re a brilliant, resourceful inventor, but you can be a bit forgetful. Well, a lot forgetful. You’ve been working on a big ball machine that’s supposed to...what was that again? It seemed so important and urgent before, but now you just can’t remember. Luckily, you always leave yourself clues in your workshop to help jog your memory. Use your ingenuity and half-finished inventions to help you remember what you needed to do. And be quick about it!
